{"tid":493193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(淫醫) 美國體操隊前隊醫涉性侵過百人, 暫已判囚60年","createTime":"2017-12-08T09:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T10:03:27.000Z","uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3065116b162daae70496925e5e3b71ae0ee7d0a5","tid":493193,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T09:29:34.000Z","msg":"不過暫只因藏兒童色情物品而判因60年, 性侵罪仲未判<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B6%89%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E9%81%8E%E7%99%BE%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7-%E8%97%8F3-7%E8%90%AC%E4%BB%B6%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E8%89%B2%E6%83%85%E7%89%A9-%E7%BE%8E%E9%AB%94%E6%93%8D%E9%9A%8A%E5%89%8D%E9%9A%8A%E9%86%AB%E5%9B%9A60%E5%B9%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%2599%25BE%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E8%2597%258F3-7%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%2585%2592%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E8%2589%25B2%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%2589%25A9-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%2593%258D%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%259A%258A%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%259B%259A60%25E5%25B9%25B4%2F&d=sx1eECieIWN3UKPoJM0ceGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=4a37d6e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%2599%25BE%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E8%2597%258F3-7%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%2585%2592%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E8%2589%25B2%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%2589%25A9-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%2593%258D%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%259A%258A%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%259B%259A60%25E5%25B9%25B4%2F&h=03d5625f\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B6%89%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E9%81%8E%E7%99%BE%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7-%E8%97%8F3-7%E8%90%AC%E4%BB%B6%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E8%89%B2%E6%83%85%E7%89%A9-%E7%BE%8E%E9%AB%94%E6%93%8D%E9%9A%8A%E5%89%8D%E9%9A%8A%E9%86%AB%E5%9B%9A60%E5%B9%B4/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n【涉性侵過百女性】藏兒童色情物品　美體操隊前隊醫囚60年<br />\n2017/12/8 &mdash; 9:36<br />\n<br />\n涉嫌性侵女子體操運動員的美國體操隊前隊醫拿沙亞（Larry Nassar），因藏有兒童色情物品罪成，周四被判60年徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n密歇根州法院法官指，54歲的拿沙亞製作、收藏的3.7萬件兒童色情物品，與他涉及多宗性侵兒童案件有關，他日後不可以再有機會接觸兒童。三項罪名各判監20年，分期執行，共判60年徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n拿沙亞還涉嫌性侵超過140名女性，包括是奧運金牌選手Aly Raisman、Gabby Douglas及McKayla Maroney。<br />\n<br />\n他上月承認承認案發於1998至2015年間的7項性侵罪，其中三項控罪指他侵犯未滿13歲的女童，根據認罪協議，拿沙亞將面臨最少25年的監禁，案件將於明年一月判刑。處理該案件法官痛斥他是利用隊醫職位所得的信任，以最卑鄙的方式侵害兒童：「我同意現在是一個癒合的時期，不過他們（受害人）可能要一輩子的時間癒合，而你或花費一輩子時間在獄中反省所作所為。」<br />\n<br />\n率先現身指證拿沙亞前體操選手德諾蘭德（Rachael Denhollander）指出，案件顯示出現由大學體育課程、以至體育團體等多個層面疏忽，指受害者一直噤聲。"},{"pid":"28b99a4632ba8659de5f9a621ad0f2cb5a494b6e","tid":493193,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T09:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22feff81db2aa3150473aa364d7e5eed7f189de","tid":493193,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"3.7萬件兒童色情物品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4e214f5851c781a19660a040a1220449e11663","tid":493193,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T10:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}